extraInfo:
For this example we use the following enum declaration:
```
    enum Size { 
        S, M, L;
        @Override String toString() {  
            switch (this) {
                case S: return "Small"
                case M: return "Medium"
                case L: return "Large"
            }
            return "?"
        }
    }
```

For this example we use the following enum declaration:
```
    enum Colour { 
        RED, GREEN, BLUE;
        @Override String toString() {  
